msg: Changed terminology based on a discussion with Igor from root to innermost and from IModelWrapper to INestedModelContainer.  These are more explicit names and affect mainly internal usage in Component and a few model classes.  These methods are renamed: sameRootModel->sameInnermostModel, getRootModel->getInnermostModel.
